</html> 404.html: <!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en"> <head> <meta charset="utf-8"> <title>Hello!</title> </head> <body> <h1>Oops!</h1> <p>Sorry, I don't know what you're asking for.</p> </body>
</html> If you run the server with cargo run and visit 127.0.0.1:7878 in your browser, you'll be greeted with a friendly message from Ferris! 如果你使用`cargo run`命令运行，并在浏览器访问`127.0.0.1:7878`，
